     {
      "id": "00000000000000000000015d",
      "title": "Changelog — 1",
      "slug": "changelog-1",
      "mobiledoc": "{\"version\": \"0.3.1\", \"atoms\": [], \"cards\": [[\"html\", {\"html\": \"<p>Somewhere between the brief and the deadline lives the actual work. This is generic demo content so you can judge the layout honestly.</p><h2 id=\\\"the-setup\\\">The setup</h2><p>Every good system starts with a constraint: frame the color 1:1, crop out the noise.</p><ul><li>Start with the audience, not the tool</li><li>Measure twice, publish once</li><li>Delete more than you add</li></ul><h2 id=\\\"the-details\\\">The details</h2><pre><code>const frame = (life) =&gt; life.filter(m =&gt; m.signal &gt; m.noise);</code></pre><blockquote>Life looks better when you frame the color 1:1.</blockquote><h3 id=\\\"wrap-up\\\">Wrap up</h3><p>If this reads well in all six theme modes, ship it.</p>\"}]], \"markups\": [], \"sections\": [[10, 0], [1, \"p\", []]]}",
